title TO ASSOCIATE USER AS TEAM MEMBER/PRODUCT OWNER/SCRUM MASTER TO A PROJECT
actor "Manager"
autonumber
"Manager" -> ":System": requests list of all User accounts
note left
Account is authenticated.
":System" grants access.
end note
